over guildsay from someone who was
there:

tells the guild, 'seems the king room here
in Sol-b has 2 groups - one that
got pissed about the waiting list or
something'

tells the guild, 'now they are trying to KS
from each other'

there gotta be 15 ppl here now!'

the waiting list are here now
and pissed off. they have formed a 3rd group
and everyone is fighting for
the room!'

Sylly Songsynger
Bard of 42 songs
<The Pantheon>
somewhere on Innoruuk...
